    728  f319							; Sub-pixel speed: accumulate the fractional speed; the carry is an
    729  f319							; extra whole pixel this frame, so the scroll step is 1 or 2 px.
    730  f319							; (scrollSpeed ramps with the score; see CheckCollision.)
