    745  f32b							; Everything below advances by scrollStep in ONE pass (O(1)) rather than a
    746  f32b							; per-pixel loop, so the overscan cost stays flat as the speed ramps -- the
    747  f32b							; per-pixel loop was up to 4x work at top speed and overran the overscan
    748  f32b							; timer (causing the screen to roll, worst on the heavier cone-pickup frame).
    749  f32b
